node.text:
Happy #WomenWednesday! 💃💪💕 Loved hanging out with Julia Haart, who you may know from @netflix original series “My Unorthodox Life”! @juliahaart is consistently disrupting the modeling industry, and helping to empower women to pursue their dreams! Sounds like my kind of chick! Let’s empower each other this #WomenWednesday and EVERY DAY! How are you empowering a woman in your life today? Let me know in the comments below ⬇️⬇️⬇️ #msbarbarak
